  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，你还记得从 Reshala 那里拿走的那把金色托卡列夫手枪吗？好吧，最近我发现有人可以制作这东西的赝品，所以当一旦你摆脱了 Reshala 的时候，我就把它们出售。\n总之，我希望你能测试一下这把枪，不管测试目标是谁都行，都是为了获得更好的测试结果，我建议你杀大约二十个Scav或PMC差不多，或者其他让你觉得厌烦的人也行。",
    "en": "Hey, do you remember the golden tokarev pistol that you took from reshala? Well, recently I found someone who can make identical copies of these things, so I put them up for sale once you got rid of reshala.\nAnyway, I want you to test this gun, doesn't matter on who, but for better results I suggest you kill about twenty bandits or operators, or someone else who gets too annoying for you."
